As of the [[census]]<ref name="GR2" /> of 2010, there were 150 people living in the CDP.  The [[population density]] was 177.18 people per square mile. The racial makeup of the CDP was:

* 86.67% [[Native American (U.S. Census)|Native American]]
* 12.38% [[White (U.S. Census)|White]]
* 3.81% [[Hispanic (U.S. Census)|Hispanic]] or [[Latino (U.S. Census)|Latino]] of any race
* 0.95% [[African American (U.S. Census)|African American]]
* 0.00% [[Pacific Islander (U.S. Census)|Pacific Islander]]
* 0.00% other races
* 0.00% of two or more races

